      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey quick question for my dissertation work. i have a result with a p-value of 0.06 in my main analysis. technically it's not significant at the .05 level, but there's a pretty clear trend in the effect size. how should i formally discuss 'noise' or randomness in the data when explaining why it missed the threshold?",
